Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.20,0:00:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在静静飘落的樱花中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.49,0:00:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做着梦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.61,0:00:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖暖的梦 幸福的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.04,0:00:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.14,0:00:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说 大家专心准备即将到来的祭典的忙碌情景
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.24,0:00:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子们的笑容 幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是身在其中 就仿佛能够忘却悲伤一般
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.03,0:00:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能一直面带笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.06,0:00:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「这一刻如果能够一直持续下去就好了」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.10,0:00:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我知道那是无法实现的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.12,0:00:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我却从心底里如此期盼着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.66,0:02:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到处都比上课时热闹很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.58,0:02:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 由梦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.73,0:02:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.09,0:02:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回家了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.39,0:02:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 现在正要去开保健委员的会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.25,0:02:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 关于圣诞派对的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.13,0:02:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 当天玩过头导致受伤的人也会很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.51,0:02:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么哥哥 我赶时间就先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.97,0:02:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮啊 朝仓同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.29,0:03:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然姐姐人气也很高 不过我还是喜欢妹妹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.38,0:03:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然看上去很可靠 不过在某方面总有一种让人担心的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.60,0:03:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错 会激起让人保护的欲望呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.64,0:03:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.10,0:03:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 真羡慕跟朝仓同学一起逛圣诞派对的那人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.41,0:03:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这一席位的竞争率貌似挺高的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.81,0:03:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 果然人气很高呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.27,0:03:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 在学校她倒是戴了十层面具呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.74,0:03:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞派对 吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.83,0:03:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 还在为如何收尾烦恼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.23,0:03:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义之你怎么想的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.48,0:03:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然还是希望看到相爱的两人最后能走到一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那样不会被说太图省事或者俗套了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.33,0:04:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是什么结局 总会有人有不同意见的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底 杏你自己想要怎么写才是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写自己想写的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.41,0:04:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我就按照自己的想法来写吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 义之
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很期待哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.02,0:04:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是关于季节的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气逐渐变冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.01,0:04:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在初音岛以樱花公园为中心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.82,0:04:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛内开始进行集体大扫除
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是初音岛观光协会每年在这一时期的惯例活动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也有来自于各自治团体的众多志愿者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忙于收集观光客遗留下来的垃圾以及空罐子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:50.92,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志愿者里也有着小朋友的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:56.84,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主办方也在这次活动中发现了很多感人的场面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:05:02.08,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初音岛观光协会也呼吁人们能够更珍惜志愿者的劳动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.32,0:05:05.42,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部分观光客也表示以后会注意自己的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.44,0:05:09.07,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是下一则新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.57,0:05:14.91,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天下午 在初音岛的购物中心发生了水管爆裂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.11,0:05:17.91,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从而导致了营业一度暂停的骚乱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.40,0:05:23.73,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据相关人士调查发现 地下的水管出现了约为两米的大裂痕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:29.14,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这一设施在半年前刚进行过水管更换
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.31,0:05:32.69,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至于水管为何会发生龟裂 实在是让人不解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.44,0:05:35.06,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正着手进行着更换工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:39.14,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至于到底有多少地方需要更换 调查仍在继续当中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:42.67,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且 购物的人并没有受到什么大伤害 购物中心…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来马上就要到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.82,0:04:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.88,0:04:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你想嘛 要在学校举行的 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.80,0:04:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个？ 是什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.76,0:05:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指的圣诞派对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 圣诞派对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊你 这么期待吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你有什么意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.36,0:05:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是没什么意见…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.26,0:05:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不吃苹果了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她这么说的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.25,0:05:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由梦说她不吃苹果了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.30,0:05:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.19,0:05:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.86,0:05:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏 难道身体不舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说她通宵在改剧本呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:05:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在到这里之前 杏一直在烦恼着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.41,0:06:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像一直睡眠不足呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.65,0:06:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近气温骤降
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意不要感冒 做好防寒措施
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请好好保重身体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.55,0:06:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外预防流行性感冒方面…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在熬夜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她父母居然什么都没说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于前些日子进行的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.93,0:06:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小杏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.59,0:06:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,38.5度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.75,0:06:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是高烧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 药已经见效 到时候自然会降下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.73,0:06:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.08,0:06:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起在这里休息 也许送她回家会比较好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.81,0:06:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么老师 接下来就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.60,0:06:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.07,0:06:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱内君 你就想这么丢下生病的女孩子不管吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.09,0:06:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说的这么难听啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就陪她到最后吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.17,0:07:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏已经没事了 药已经起效 她睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.26,0:07:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过不知为何演变成了要我送杏回家这一情况了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？小杏家？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.55,0:07:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我们也从没去过呢 小杏家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.51,0:07:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.69,0:07:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可真是意外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.70,0:07:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是这附近才对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.21,0:07:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.36,0:07:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.68,0:07:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.85,0:07:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可真是吓人一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:07:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙关照
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:08:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来在把你交给你父母前都应该是我的工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们都不在家…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 樱内君真的可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.27,0:08:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么说是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有义之就别无所求了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.64,0:08:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「别无所求」…你们俩这是在搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你记得好好睡一觉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师也请路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫消失啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.21,0:08:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 还是吃点什么比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你午饭也没吃吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好像什么也没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.94,0:09:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我家有对味道很挑剔的人在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.35,0:09:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用你家冰箱里的东西做的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.66,0:09:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在笑什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.26,0:09:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又帮我做稀饭 又帮我吹凉了让我吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟很久以前的我奶奶一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.71,0:09:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来你家里人还没回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个家是不会有人回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.15,0:09:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 从小时候起便被双亲抛弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.07,0:09:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了很多事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.73,0:09:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后奶奶收留了我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.69,0:10:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪村便是那个把我作为养女收养了的奶奶的姓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.85,0:10:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个奶奶呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年前去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.35,0:10:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在我即将进入风见学园的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那之后 我便一直一个人生活在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.64,0:10:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 跟你说这么沉重的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 没什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.96,0:10:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的 不用勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.05,0:10:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不想让人替我操无谓的心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.12,0:10:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才没有对任何人讲起过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连茜跟小恋也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.14,0:10:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在杏身上 有过这样的往事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.62,0:10:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今天起这里就是你家了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.45,0:10:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这里是我哥哥的家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 大家都是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.45,0:11:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然在没有父母这一点上我也是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.42,0:11:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我身边还有由梦跟音姐她们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.26,0:11:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她却…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进展如何呢 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.98,0:11:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当天要做些什么已经定下来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做些什么指的是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.13,0:11:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所 所以嘛 就是指的 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.93,0:11:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有要跟你一起逛的人 什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.71,0:11:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 现在还没定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.24,0:11:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.15,0:11:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 由梦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.82,0:11:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.30,0:11:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.60,0:11:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁还没忘之前给你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.67,0:11:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥 哥哥 这难道是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.31,0:12:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？ 不要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.12,0:12:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 也不是不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么拿着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真 真拿你没办法呢 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.64,0:12:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别 别误会了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.76,0:12:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是因为哥哥你说要给我 没办法才…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.99,0:12:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两张？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.33,0:12:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有跟你一起逛的那人的份
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.41,0:12:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真 真是感谢你了 这份好意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.01,0:12:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}「醒了的话记得吃了 义之」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.87,0:12:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义之…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.93,0:13:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏身上 有过这样的往事啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.39,0:13:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不想让你们操无谓的心 所以一直没说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小杏真见外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.17,0:13:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得还是告诉你们比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.43,0:13:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you 义之君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.58,0:13:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.31,0:13:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.04,0:13:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不要紧了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.28,0:13:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好些了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.79,0:13:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.04,0:13:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.90,0:13:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.57,0:13:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天休息一天比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.71,0:13:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练习的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.54,0:13:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜欢给大家添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.11,0:13:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 对我的身体更不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.04,0:13:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就知道你这么说 杏还是老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.94,0:13:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.20,0:13:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这么办吧 你身体状态也还不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.53,0:13:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就到你家去练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.20,0:13:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便说说 觉得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.68,0:13:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.95,0:14:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家聚在一起会比较愉快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.97,0:14:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.33,0:14:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想让大家担心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.55,0:14:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的想法我很理解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 怎么说呢 对我们不要那么见外才好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.84,0:14:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义之
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.43,0:14:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.24,0:14:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先邀请大家去家里怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.01,0:14:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也好想去小杏家呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.78,0:14:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.08,0:14:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就这样吧 去我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.03,0:14:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小杏的家 好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.01,0:14:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.59,0:14:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是杏家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.78,0:14:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壮观
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:15:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离我家很近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.20,0:15:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 太棒了 充满阳光 微风 和绿意盎然的雪村家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.25,0:15:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 杉並 你什么时候来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.48,0:15:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈 不用吓成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.59,0:15:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.72,0:15:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.05,0:15:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是小杏的房间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 比想像中的要还要荒凉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.85,0:15:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的环境我会比较安心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.23,0:15:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真意外
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.57,0:15:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.30,0:15:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏不是成绩很好么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.69,0:15:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房间里应该堆上一大堆书才合理嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.80,0:15:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不藏书的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为看一遍就全部记住了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.68,0:15:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记忆力真强大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.93,0:15:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是只有好处的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 开始练习了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得来一次 先玩会儿嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.83,0:15:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:15:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们 忘了来干什么的了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.03,0:16:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.01,0:16:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了 雪村流记忆术
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.57,0:16:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来玩什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.02,0:16:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扑克吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.16,0:16:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.42,0:16:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 练习怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.97,0:16:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连杏也起劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至 至尊同花顺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.32,0:16:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.68,0:16:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计算一下剩下和已经出的牌 还有每个人的出牌习惯就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.01,0:16:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 大功告成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.97,0:16:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练习什么时候才开始啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饿着肚子可没法干活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.59,0:16:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得没错 料理就交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.73,0:16:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏你也来帮帮忙呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只负责卖萌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.39,0:16:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饱了饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粗茶淡饭 不成敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.94,0:17:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.88,0:17:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好极了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还在想咖喱怎么不放土豆太邪门了 没想到味道不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜谱可是杏提供的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.96,0:17:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是把以前看过的菜谱创新了下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.48,0:17:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来创新才是王道啊 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.53,0:17:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 说到底人的创新全是靠前人经验的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.41,0:17:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有话说天下文章一大抄嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.22,0:17:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个说得太极端了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.93,0:17:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个那个 知不知道咖喱饭和盖浇咖喱的区别
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.37,0:17:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.26,0:17:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来练习要泡汤了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.84,0:17:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖喱多就是咖喱饭 饭多就是盖浇咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.79,0:17:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.77,0:17:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义之
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.15,0:17:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然发现你不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.73,0:18:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微安静下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.56,0:18:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不擅长和人接触吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.24,0:18:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.20,0:18:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像在海里游了一天 晚上闭起眼睛会觉得还在海浪里漂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.38,0:18:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.12,0:18:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单说 就是很愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道这样 应该早点邀请大家来玩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.87,0:18:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情都要一步步来的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.28,0:18:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始没能完全接受奶奶的死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.14,0:18:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次提起这件事 都害怕回想起往事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才一直没说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.32,0:18:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经过了三年了 终于心情也平稳下来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.08,0:18:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 错过了说出口的机会倒是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:18:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候 我正好碰巧来到杏家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.99,0:19:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有空再来玩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.72,0:19:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.54,0:19:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拿着纸牌干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.92,0:19:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.17,0:19:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是义之在背后推了我一把
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.10,0:19:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞派对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.85,0:19:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.42,0:19:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥…哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞派对就要到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.23,0:20:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.54,0:20:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由梦决定和谁一起逛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.63,0:20:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么和谁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.05,0:20:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在男生都痴狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.10,0:20:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你人气还是挺高的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.60,0:20:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我还没决定和谁一起逛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.87,0:20:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.10,0:20:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有中意的对象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认识的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.82,0:20:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由梦不好意思开口的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.06,0:20:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以帮你去说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.57,0:20:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.78,0:20:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别客气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.33,0:20:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不用了 我东西还没买完
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.82,0:20:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.84,0:20:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.82,0:21:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来这次事又闹大了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.00,0:21:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也能用魔法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.93,0:21:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你也能用魔法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.03,0:21:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.68,0:21:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正义的魔法使
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.42,0:23:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昔日的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.93,0:23:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍重的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.09,0:23:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柔弱的肩膀上所背负的是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.28,0:23:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉重的使命
